# Media Stack Monitoring

This document describes the monitoring integration for the media stack, including:
- Prometheus metrics
- Grafana dashboards
- Loki log aggregation
- Telegraf metrics collection
- Health checks
- Alerting and notification channels

## Metrics
- Service up/down
- CPU usage
- Memory usage
- Disk usage
- Failed downloads

## Dashboards
- Grafana dashboard: media-stack-dashboard.json

## Alerts
- Service down
- High CPU
- High memory
- Failed downloads

## Log aggregation
- Loki configuration for all media services

## Maintenance
- Monitoring and metrics scripts are scheduled via cron
- Systemd service for continuous monitoring 